org.cpsolver.ifs.extension

Class AssignedValue<T extends Value<?,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.extension.AssignedValue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Value

    public class AssignedValue<T extends Value<?,T>>
extends Object
    This class describing an assignment of a value to a variable together with a counter (used by CBS). Counter also supports aging: the counter is multiplied by aging factor for each iteration.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)

      • revise

        public void revise(long iteration)
        Revise counter. If aging is used, counter is adopted to the current iteration: it is multiplied by aging factor powered by the number of iterations since last revision.
        Parameters:
        iteration - current iteration
